reviewText: Really nice trio of movies with Harrison Ford.  Loved them all.
If you love Harrison Ford this is a great buy!!
Harrison Ford always "brings it" and this is a great collection!
I'ts all good...WoW..really he's a serial killer...
3 really well done Ford movies.....Patriot Games is the best of the 3, but the other 2 are extremely well done...
Sold as used but arrived with packaging unopened. Unable to review- given away as a gift.
